<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Stay</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/stay.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

</head>
<body>
  <section class="first">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>ORCHID HOTELS</h1>
        <div class="search-box">
  <input type="text" id="search-bar" placeholder="Search for Destinations or Hotels">
  <button id="search-btn">Search</button>
</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="title">EXPLORE ORCHID</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">
          From a luxury urban sanctum to the halls of royalty, our 5-star hotels and luxury resorts bring your imagination to life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="second">
    <div class="container1">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/hotel3.jpeg" alt="Ocean View Retreat">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="hotel-name">ORCHID VIEW RETREATS, MUMBAI</h3>
          <p>Experience timeless elegance at The Pierre, where orchid's hospitality meets New York's luxury, offering sophistication and classic charm</p>
          <form action="/hotel/<%= encodeURIComponent('ORCHID VIEW RETREATS, MUMBAI') %>" method="GET">
            <button class="book-now">BOOK NOW</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/hotel2.jpeg" alt="Orchid Palace">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="hotel-name" >ORCHID HOTEL, GOA</h3>
          <p>Immerse in London's history and style at St. James' Court, a orchid Hotel, offering a blend of Victorian grandeur and contemporary luxury</p>
          <form action="/hotel/<%= encodeURIComponent('ORCHID HOTEL, GOA') %>" method="GET">
            <button class="book-now">BOOK NOW</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/hotel4.jpeg" alt="Orchid Palace">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="hotel-name" >ORCHID HOTELS, HYDERABAD</h3>
          <p>Explore luxury and elegance at Taj Krishna, Hyderabad, where impeccable service, sumptuous dining, and opulent accommodations define your stay</p>
          <form action="/hotel/<%= encodeURIComponent('ORCHID HOTELS, HYDERABAD') %>" method="GET">
            <button class="book-now">BOOK NOW</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/hotel5.jpeg" alt="Orchid Palace">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="hotel-name" >ORCHID HOTEL, BENGALURU</h3>
          <p>Amidst lush gardens, the Taj West End is a sanctuary of elegance in Bengaluru, boasting a heritage walk, exquisite dining and an aura of timeless sophistication.</p>
          <form action="/hotel/<%= encodeURIComponent('ORCHID HOTEL, BENGALURU') %>" method="GET">
            <button class="book-now">BOOK NOW</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/hotel1.jpeg" alt="Orchid Palace">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="hotel-name" >ORCHID HOTEL, DUBAI</h3>
          <p>Surrender to luxury on The Palm at Exotica, where Arabian elegance, pristine beaches, and indulgent moments define your Dubai getaway</p>
          <form action="/hotel/<%= encodeURIComponent('ORCHID HOTEL, DUBAI') %>" method="GET">
            <button class="book-now">BOOK NOW</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/hotel6.jpeg" alt="Mountain Bliss">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="hotel-name" >ORCHID MOUNTAIN BLISS, LEH</h3>
          <p>Find peace and serenity in the lap of the mountains.</p>
          <form action="/hotel/<%= encodeURIComponent('ORCHID MOUNTAIN BLISS, LEH') %>" method="GET">
            <button class="book-now">BOOK NOW</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="third">
    <div class="food-section">
      <div class="heading">
        <span class="divider"></span>
        <h2>EXCLUSIVE <br> EXPERIENCE</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="description">
        <p>
          Indulge in unparalleled luxury with our Exclusively for You section, offering bespoke experiences tailored to elevate your stay. From personalized services to premium amenities, we ensure every moment is truly special.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="deck-container">
      <input class="select-toggle" type="radio" name="selection" id="cardOne" checked />
      <label class="card-box" for="cardOne">
        <h3 class="additional-info"><span>GREAT ROOMS</span></h3>
      </label>

      <input class="select-toggle" type="radio" name="selection" id="cardTwo" />
      <label class="card-box" for="cardTwo">
        <h3 class="additional-info"><span>GRAND HALLWAYS</span></h3>
      </label>

      <input class="select-toggle" type="radio" name="selection" id="cardThree" />
      <label class="card-box" for="cardThree">
        <h3 class="additional-info"><span>SERENADE SWIM</span></h3>
      </label>

      <input class="select-toggle" type="radio" name="selection" id="cardFour" />
      <label class="card-box" for="cardFour">
        <h3 class="additional-info"><span>EXQUISITE VIEW</span></h3>
      </label>
    </div>
  </section>
  <footer class="footer" id="about">
    <div class="footer-container">
      <div class="footer-section logo-social">
        <img src="/images/logomain.png" alt="Logo" class="footer-logo" />
        <p>Your luxury getaway awaits. Relax, dine, and enjoy.</p>
        <div class="social-icons">
          <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
          <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
          <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="footer-section quick-links">
        <h3>Quick Links</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#stay">Stay</a></li>
          <li><a href="#dining">Dining</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
  
      <div class="footer-section contact-info">
        <h3>Contact</h3>
        <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> 123 Beachside Avenue, Goa</p>
        <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +91 98765 43210</p>
        <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> info@luxehotel.com</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="footer-section map-section">
        <h3>Find Us</h3>
        <div class="map-container">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d241317.11609944104!2d72.7410993215829!3d19.082522317140222!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3be7b63a30ecfab5%3A0xf9347e564d3706aa!2sGoa!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1615377511097!5m2!1sen!2sin"
            width="100%" height="150" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2025 LuxeHotel. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
  <script>
    
  document.getElementById("search-btn").addEventListener("click", function () {
    const query = document.getElementById("search-bar").value.toLowerCase();
    const cards = document.querySelectorAll(".card");

    cards.forEach(card => {
      const name = card.querySelector(".hotel-name").textContent.toLowerCase();
      card.style.display = name.includes(query) ? "block" : "none";
    });
  });
</script>

  <script src="/js/storage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>